      <title>独家：欧佩克秘书长认为长期需求前景强劲</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/opec-sec-gen-firmly-believes-published-long-term-demand-outlook-robust-2024-02-13/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧佩克秘书长周二表示，沙特阿拉伯推迟石油产能扩张计划的决定不应被解读为对原油需求下降的评估。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/opec-sec-gen-firmly-believes-published-long-term-demand-outlook-robust-2024-02-13/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 09:06:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
